{"tid":1574775,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"比獨裁者更不堪的賤民 - 高慧然","createTime":"2019-09-16T14:43:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-16T15:01:00.000Z","uid":25558,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"4772d3289bb12bdcc175d74dc4900ea7f68bc1c3","tid":1574775,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T14:43:32.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/%E9%AB%98%E6%85%A7%E7%84%B6/daily/article/20190916/20768816\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%25E9%25AB%2598%25E6%2585%25A7%25E7%2584%25B6%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190916%2F20768816&d=9iHhAbkmMxvvE1I2I23sbTr7MFgrQ0V0XG6LyL0fmAc%3D&h=ed836c33\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%25E9%25AB%2598%25E6%2585%25A7%25E7%2584%25B6%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190916%2F20768816&h=690eb9af\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/%E9%AB%98%E6%85%A7%E7%84%B6/daily/article/20190916/20768816</a><br />\n<br />\n比獨裁者更不堪的賤民 - 高慧然<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple_sub/20190916/large/1568532150_798c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple_sub%2F20190916%2Flarge%2F1568532150_798c.jpg&h=69233fd1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n法新社(法新社)<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n網傳李婉華在加拿大中文電台主持節目時，播出香港爆紅的歌曲《願榮光歸香港》，結果引起眾多「移民加拿大的愛國港人」投訴，被迫封咪。我第一時間去問加拿大的朋友，朋友找到節目總監求證，證實李婉華封咪是誤傳，但聽眾投訴卻是事實。<br />\n<br />\n無法點算投訴者之中，有多少個是「移民加拿大的愛國中國人」，有多少個是「移民加拿大的愛國港人」，但兩者之中，論卑賤程度，以後者更甚。<br />\n<br />\n中國人目光短淺如豆，易為利益驅動，很多人移民外國，不一定出於政治考量，純粹是為了生活。但香港人移民加拿大，肯定不是因為加拿大比香港更容易賺錢，反而是政治考量居多。我認識的朋友之中，很多是六四之後痛別香港，捨棄高薪厚職，去加拿大艱難創業的。他們避秦成功，入了加國國籍，拿着加國護照，享受着當地的自由、法治、民主、人權，隔岸觀火，看到被剝奪自由、法治、民主、人權的香港人奮力反抗暴政，抵抗六四2.0的時候，卻站在獨裁政權的一面，打壓香港人。這種人，連基本的良知都已經滅絕。<br />\n<br />\n「移民加拿大的愛國港人」是多麼奇怪的物種，明明是香港人，明明愛中國，卻移民去了加拿大，向加拿大宣誓效忠，這誓言有幾成是真的？我親耳聽過一個六四後移民加拿大的香港人跟我說，「我在電視看到學生被殺，腳都軟了，當夜決定移民。」也就是這同一個人，前些日子跟我說，「中國現在經濟很好了，香港人為甚麼還要反共？」 <br />\n<br />\n高慧然<br />\n電郵 :kowaiyin2004@yahoo.com.hk<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n林鄭的靠山 (尊子)<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n下一則<br />\n721，831接二連三 (陳也)"},{"pid":"b1b5fae7777a58c7688077e41fbbcca1c0a45033","tid":1574775,"uid":263058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T14:44:39.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"31514a78980b4880a476d0aa04fcf59568e194a8","tid":1574775,"uid":33930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T14:44:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pvsTHEi.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpvsTHEi.jpg&h=e8bfe3ea&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">宣佈 和你suck 4.0 9月22 星期日見<br />\n<br />\nsuck 4.0 將會基於 hkmap.live 行動  <br />\n麻煩力推呢個livemap <br />\n對各位日後行動都非常大幫助<br />\n<br />\n請各位必須係 9月22日當日12點30分留意channel / 連登 / IG 最新消息<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n連登post:<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1568754\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1568754</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n TG : <a href=\"https://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyou&d=9iHhAbkmMxvvE1I2I23sbTr7MFgrQ0V0XG6LyL0fmAc%3D&h=21ee496d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/stuckwithyou</a><br />\n<br />\nIG : <a href=\"https://instagram.com/suck.withyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Finstagram.com%2Fsuck.withyou&d=9iHhAbkmMxvvE1I2I23sbTr7MFgrQ0V0XG6LyL0fmAc%3D&h=f965b405\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://instagram.com/suck.withyou</a></span>"},{"pid":"5058944e014ecbb048171ce86edf10a808ded48e","tid":1574775,"uid":173058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"31514a78980b4880a476d0aa04fcf59568e194a8","tid":1574775,"uid":33930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T14:44:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pvsTHEi.jpg\" data